actions.message:
There are some rules you might want to follow, it's not too strict, we all want to have fun:

1. Be friendly
2. Show respect to everyone
3. Do not spam, includes tagging people, they don't want to hear the ping sound
4. Channels are created for purposes, depends on channel name and topic, don't spam a bot on ${tempVars("channel")}, use in ${tempVars("channel2")} instead
5. No political or religious topics
6. No NSFW and gore, permaban immediately!
7. We don't accept any report if you got scammed by other members
8. Posting virus or any unknown link will also result a ban
9. Read the pinned messages in text channels, there are some extra things
10. Have fun
actions.name: Send Message

actions.message:
The leveling system is pretty easy to understand thanks to **Tatsumaki**
You will earn a random amount of server exp from 10-20
The cooldown is 2 minutes, so you can't spam
You can check your exp by typing `trank` or `tprofile` in ${tempVars("channel")}
